- Every model number you reference must appear verbatim in the source materials.
- Every contact name must appear in the email headers provided.
- Do not make date commitments unless the exact date appears in the source.
- If a value is not explicitly sourced, omit it and flag with NEEDS_BRAD_INPUT.
- word_count must be an accurate count of the draft_body text.
- confidence: HIGH = all values sourced, MEDIUM = minor gaps flagged, LOW = significant gaps.

